{"tid":320922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國一些參議員質疑 劉曉波當天去世 川普卻大讚習近平 很不恰當","createTime":"2017-07-14T01:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T01:40:33.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7254e438f01a959da268847d69f784543c719686","tid":320922,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"川普馬克宏談習近平 川普對習讚不絕口  <br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普和法國總統馬克宏13日在巴黎舉行聯合記者會，一位中國大陸記者問兩位總 統對大陸國家主席習近平的看法，<span style=\"color: red;\">川普表示，他和習近平是朋友，他很尊敬習，兩人很熟 ，習近平很有才華，是個好人，他很愛中國。</span>川普還說，習近平是很特別的人。 馬克宏表示，他在漢堡G20高峰會上與習近平會談，兩人不算熟，稱不上朋友，但他很尊 敬習近平，他還說，習近平是了不起的領袖。 CNN記者指出，兩位總統只回答四個問題，按理應接受美國和法國記者提問，但卻接受一 位大陸記者提問，很不尋常。 <span style=\"color: red;\">美國一些參議員則質疑，大陸異議人士劉曉波當天去世，川普卻大讚習近平，很不恰當</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2582605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F2582605&d=%2BO3k%2BPpaLnRfGuh6YzXbMIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a2fda036\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2582605</a>"},{"pid":"186fa7e933aaa2155684be4850fd93448ae121f0","tid":320922,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e48fb784bb1183c4ac6fc029b4719cdf5fb2d12","tid":320922,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"美國總統？真係一只畜牲"},{"pid":"958af1d18cf2150ffb47c34d165d9f81e02b0b48","tid":320922,"uid":14482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45a9d7ec344337c86fcadeb133cd1a05307c4198","tid":320922,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4aee300176a102b0c4127071be1afc3add2f969c","tid":320922,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"條友講嘢唔經大腦，鍾意嗡乜就乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}